de.k3b.geo.api

Interface IGeoRepository<R extends IGeoPointInfo>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeoFileRepository

    public interface IGeoRepository<R extends IGeoPointInfo>

    Abstract Repository to load/save List<IGeoPointInfo > .

    It can be used for GeoPointDto or any custom IGeoPointInfo implementation.

    Created by k3b on 17.03.2015.
